## ğŸ› ï¸ Setup

### Hardware
- Arduino Uno R3
- Analog joystick
- Push button
- 220Î© resistor for the LED
- Jumper wires, breadboard

### Software
1. Flash Arduino with the joystick + button code.
2. Open the browser game (index.html) on your computer.
3. Make sure your serial port is selected in browser.
4. Blast some asteroids!

